data.meta_description: VAN FLEET JO: (1914-1996) American actress, Academy Award winner for Best Supporting Actress in 1955 for her role as Kate in East of Eden. Signed 10 x 8 photograph of Van Fleet standing outdoors in a half-length pose, in costume from her Oscar winning performance as the brothel keeper Kate, as she engages in conversation with James Dean, in costume as Kate's son, Caleb Trask. Signed by Van Fleet in bold blue ink with her name alone to the lower white border. VG
